            <title>[SPARK-39218] Python foreachBatch streaming query cannot be stopped gracefully after pin thread mode is enabled</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-39218</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;For example,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; time

def func(batch_df, batch_id):
    time.sleep(10)
    print(batch_df.count())

q = spark.readStream.format(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;rate&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).load().writeStream.foreachBatch(func).start()
time.sleep(5)
q.stop()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

